@mikebond6328 Oh yes. Just 9% (30 vols) will be fine. Hair bleaching cream also works. Be a good idea for you to view on youtube this video for some tips and warning first. 
“Retr0bright - de-yellowing do's, dont's, and playing devil's advocate”
Some recommend UV light but this can brake the plastic’s polymer chains, causing the plastic to become brittle — so avoid.
